dct_description_sm: "3728." Includes location map, key, key map and text. In upper margin: N.J. coast map vol. 3 Sheets 24 and 85-87 of N.J. coast map, vol. 3, series, originally issued in 1905; sheet 24: New sheet, Apr. 1921; sheets 85-87: Add'l sheets, Apr. 1921.
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Sanborn Map Company, 1921, c1905.
